dfischer.utils

Class DataCollectionYZFloatItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.DataCollectionAbstractItem
      • dfischer.utils.DataCollectionYZFloatItem

  • public class DataCollectionYZFloatItem
extends DataCollectionAbstractItem
    Measured data item which contains two float values and a time stamp (X-axis = time stamp, Y-axis = float value 1, Z-axis = float value 2).
    See Also:
    DataCollectionAbstractItem.ITEM_TYPE_YZ_FLOAT_VALUE, DataCollectionSequence
